  @par Reference(s):
  - PCI Firmware Specification - Revision 3.3
  - ACPI 6.4 specification:
   - s6.2.13 "_PRT (PCI Routing Table)"
   - s6.1.1 "_ADR (Address)"
  - linux kernel code
